The following events took place in '''4056 [[Galactic Standard Calendar|BBY]]'''.

==Events==
*The [[Dynamet Corporation]] donated a large sum of credits to the hospital [[Dynamet General Hospital|Mercy General]] on Taris for the construction of a wing devoted to curing the [[Rakghoul plague/Legends|rakghoul plague]]. The hospital was renamed Dynamet General in thanks. {{Circa}}<ref name="Dynamet General">{{TORcite|type=codex|Dynamet General}}</ref>
*Around this time, [[Tarisian Civil War|civil war]] broke out between the Tarisian nobility and the planet's largely [[Alien/Legends|alien]] lower class. The conflict was sparked when rising levels of toxic pollution poisoned the planet's oceans and famine swept the city-world, and the nobility began to hoard food for themselves. Though the lower classes rose up against the nobility, the rebellion was ultimately crushed after millions died in the fighting.<ref name="KOTOR">''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic]]''</ref> The prisons in the upper levels ran out of space for the surplus of incarcerated citizens, and thus the practice of casting criminals to the [[Undercity (Taris)|Undercity]] was born. They could not return under penalty of death.

